description:
Wentworth - S02E07 - Metamorphosis

When Ferguson takes her revenge on the prisoners by bulldozing the garden project, Doreen turns her anger on Franky. Ferguson psychologically manipulates Vera and she crosses a point of no return whilst Maxine orchestrates a desperate bid to see her spurned lover. Bea sets in motion her final, audacious plan to exact revenge on Brayden Holt.
